  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7552002">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7552002/" class="title-link">文字什么的，都显得苍白无力了</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7552002"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/68506415/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u68506415-6.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/68506415/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">HR</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-07-29"
      class="main-meta">2015-07-29 12:00:09</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7552002_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  老树，这个名字就让人特别的感动，朴实，而且外看似枯槁，其实年轮层层是扎扎实实。老树的绿是深刻的绿，油墨绿，老树的画看一眼心波动，再看一眼心感动。  安安静静，对世界呈静默观望状。就已经是非常好的意境。  文字什么的，都显得苍白无力了。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">8有用 / 0没用</span>
